.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-INSPECT" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-inspect \- Inspect the normalized runtime plan
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose inspect [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Show the normalized runtime plan derived from the compose specification. Use verbose mode when you need cache, mount, or resolved environment details.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB-f\fR, \fB--file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose specification file to read; if omitted, use the active context compose file or fall back to compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--verbose\fR
Include resolved environment values and final mount mappings.
.TP
\fB--tree\fR
Show services as a dependency tree.
.TP
\fB--rightsize\fR
Compare requested resources against tracked post\-run usage and suggest conservative replacements.
.TP
\fB--dependencies\fR
Show the normalized service dependency graph.
.TP
\fB--dependencies\-format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Dependency graph output format. Default: text. Possible values: text, dot.
.TP
\fB--job\-id\fR \fIJOB_ID\fR
Tracked Slurm job id to right\-size instead of the latest recorded submission.
.TP
\fB--sstat\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sstat executable for \-\-rightsize. Default: sstat.
.TP
\fB--squeue\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the squeue executable for \-\-rightsize. Default: squeue.
.TP
\fB--sacct\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sacct executable for \-\-rightsize. Default: sacct.
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose inspect \-f compose.yaml
hpc\-compose inspect \-\-verbose \-f compose.yaml
hpc\-compose inspect \-f compose.yaml \-\-format json
.fi
